data.description: A MUST-SEE home just outside of Lawton / Fort Sill, located in Cache school district. This approximately 2300 square foot home boasts with beauty. Upon walking in, you are greeted with an extremely spacious open living space with a glorious fireplace as a focal point. It features extravagant finishes from the trim to the walls, wood plank ceramic tile floors, and gorgeous granite countertops in all of the bathrooms, the kitchen, and the laundry room. This home has 5 large bedrooms and 3 full baths. One bath is a Jack and Jill bath between 2 of the bedrooms, keeping a separate sink on either Jack and Jill side. The home features lots of storage space and big, built-in closets, until you get to the primary suite with the closet so grand you could fit a bed in! That particular closet has three levels of shelving, drawers, and racks. The primary bath features a vast six-foot whirlpool tub and a separate commode area. Spacious bedrooms and living space continue to charm the rest of the house, but matching in greatness is the huge, fenced-in yard! Schedule a showing so you don'1t miss out!! Call Courtney at 814.366.4250
